      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can temporarily patch up a broken weapon or technological item to suppress the penalties from the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.0yJjfyvWg5pDLcVR.JournalEntryPage.qtS73Nr2s2OvQadu]{Broken} condition for 1 minute per mechanic level. This does not restore any Hit Points to the item, and it does not function on an item reduced to 0 Hit Points. Additionally, when filling the engineer role during starship combat, once per combat you can perform the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.starship-actions.B9CsbXIcE9ZGlGv9]{Hold It Together} action in the same round you perform another engineering action.</p>"
